:FED.
1.3 Betalingsservice pre-notification
:SKRSLUT.
.br
1.3.1 Information of future payments will appear from a list found under
"future payments" in &WEBSYSNAVN.. In addition, the customer will receive
his or her Betalingsservice pre-notifications by ordinary mail or
electronically, see below.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
1.4. Electronic payment information
:SKRSLUT.
.br
1.4.1 If the customer has registered with electronic mail (e-Boks) via the
&WEBSYSNAVN. agreement, he or she will receive electronic payment
information in e-Boks and will no longer be entitled to receive printed
Betalingsservice pre-notifications. However, if it deems it to be
necessary, &BANKNAVN. may choose to also send printed Betalingsservice
pre-notifications to the customer. If the customer has registered with
electronic mail (e-Boks) and specifically wishes to receive printed
Betalingsservice pre-notifications, he or she may enter into agreement with
&BANKNAVN. to such effect.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
1.5 Termination of BS mandates
:SKRSLUT.
.br
1.5.1 The customer may cancel BS mandates via &WEBSYSNAVN.. Cancelled BS
mandates will not be included in the list of BS mandates in &WEBSYSNAVN..
